OL,6,FThe number of deaths related to
OL,7,Falcohol in Scotland is at a 15-year
OL,8,Fhigh, new figures have revealed.
OL,10,FLast year, 1,276 deaths were
OL,11,Fattributed to 'alcohol-specific
OL,12,Fcauses' - 31 more than in 2021, and
OL,13,Fthe highest number since 2008.
OL,15,Fdeaths related to alcohol were
OL,16,Frecorded in Scotland in 2022.
OL,18,FMale deaths continued to account for
OL,19,Faround two thirds of the figures.
OL,3,CAlcohol-related deaths in Scotland
OL,4,Creach highest levels since 2008
